relevant_findings.general: Alert, well-appearing, and in no apparent distress
relevant_findings.ears_nose_throat: Ears and nose without visible erythema, masses, or trauma. Oropharynx without visible lesion, erythema or exudate
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Heart regular, tachycardic, no murmur, no S3, no S4, no JVD.
relevant_findings.respiratory: Lungs clear to auscultation with good air movement bilaterally. Breathing is non-labored.
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Abdomen soft, non-distended, + left-sided TTP mild. Bowel sounds present. No HSM.
relevant_findings.extremities: No cyanosis, clubbing, or edema; warm.
